# Session [26] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Firewall chist?  
- Tarze kar Firewall  
- Estefadeh-ha dar network  

## Flashback – Firewall Basics
- Firewall = device ya software ke **traffic ro monitor va filter mikonad**  
- Baraye security va prevent kardan access haye unauthorized estefade mishavad  

## Explanation

### Tarze Kar
- Firewall rules ro bar asas IP, port, protocol, application moshakhas mikonad  
- Traffic incoming va outgoing check mishavad  
- Allow ya deny mikonad bar asas policy  

### Types of Firewall
- **Packet Filtering Firewall** → traffic ro bar asas source/destination IP & port check mikonad  
- **Stateful Firewall** → track mikonad state connection ha va rule ha ro apply mikonad  
- **Application Firewall** → traffic application layer (HTTP, FTP) ro monitor mikonad  

### Example Table
| Type                   | Function                                   | Use Case |
|------------------------|-------------------------------------------|----------|
| Packet Filtering       | Check IP & Port                            | Basic security |
| Stateful Inspection    | Track connection state                     | Enterprise LAN |
| Application Layer      | Monitor apps (HTTP, FTP)                   | Web security |

### Estefadeh-ha
- Protection dar LAN va WAN  
- Prevent unauthorized access  
- Control traffic baraye performance va security  

